result.name: Billidart Restaurant & Bar

reviews.text: Have pool table, darts, beer pong and slap cup. Not many choices in wanchai with so many facilities in one place. A bit overpriced in general
Fast service and good food.  Came for lunch for the first time.  Nice ambiance,  with pool tables and dart boards.
Super rude staff! They added bar snack charges to our bill without asking if we wanted them, then argued with us about it. Better darts places elsewhere.
Really cheap during happy hour! Great pool tables, howerver cocktails could be better.
This is a good drinking and relaxing place
